{"tid":2476887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微信女扮長情慫恿買比特幣 　呃走失婚漢11萬元兼不知所終","createTime":"2021-04-06T00:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T21:14:37.000Z","uid":271829,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"b890d0f59a3d54ece6a5f9ca65372888d95cd975","tid":2476887,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T00:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xI-5zcHSKFGVkNXheWAU6G80BXg=/802x1052/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VJUSDHUCWVH5ZBTPB5ASCHPZDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxI-5zcHSKFGVkNXheWAU6G80BXg%3D%2F802x1052%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVJUSDHUCWVH5ZBTPB5ASCHPZDM.jpg&h=cc97067f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡女樣貌甜美，男事主承認曾欲追求她。事主提供<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-9qg58c0wuGnuH99VrTad46LJvE=/802x1173/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O4MT2I7D55C3ZKNEDJX6KHG5UM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-9qg58c0wuGnuH99VrTad46LJvE%3D%2F802x1173%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO4MT2I7D55C3ZKNEDJX6KHG5UM.jpg&h=bbf52e33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡女經常傳送生活照給事主。事主提供<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hjhjVfq1HT17evv5Qyld4gx0Z48=/802x1198/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CRGIBM3O75DTRMK55JJTOSAF7I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhjhjVfq1HT17evv5Qyld4gx0Z48%3D%2F802x1198%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCRGIBM3O75DTRMK55JJTOSAF7I.jpg&h=26d151fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男事主懷疑慘墮愛情陷阱，上月13日前往天水圍警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n比特幣價格屢創新高，催生騙案！44歲失婚漢為追尋「第二春」，慘中美人計陷阱！一年前他在一個交友程式認識一名長腿美女，慫恿他投資比特幣（Bitcoin），又以「放電式」的甜言蜜語誘他落疊，他以為找到真愛，兩個月前把11萬元交給對方投資，結果失聯無影，他懷疑受騙報警，暫未有人被捕，男事主自嘲衰戇居，以為對方這些年的情話是真心真意。<br />\n<br />\n事主姓李（44歲），與前妻育有一子一女，2008年離婚，子女由前妻撫養，自己獨居元朗洪福邨一單位。李任職倉務員，月入約兩萬元。去年5月15日，李透過內地一個交友程式「探探」認識一名姓蔡港女，報稱在本港一間控股公司做代理，幫人投資比特幣及黃金，李承認見蔡女樣貌娟好，欲進一步發展。<br />\n兩人一直靠微信傳情，蔡女不斷游說他投資比特幣，聲稱可以賺大錢，希望一起成立一個發展基金，並言「我唔係人哋，我可能係你將來嘅另一半」、「如果冇屬於我哋的基金點開始」，更不時把生活照及露出長腿的性感照給李。<br />\n兩人在微信交往約一年，今年1月7日才第一次見面，當日相約在觀塘飲下午茶，李見蔡女貌似老實，放下戒心答應投資，夜晚再約見面，先把3萬元交予蔡女投資，這也是最後一次見面，其後再把7萬元交付蔡的女秘書。至同月21日，他透過櫃員機再過了1萬元給蔡女，前後共涉款11萬元。<br />\n李表示，過數後蔡女曾向他展示一個擺放金額「投資戶口」，並不斷要求李加碼，但李坦言沒有積蓄。其後，蔡女便開始變面，漸漸疏遠他，李察覺有異，遂要求取回11萬元，蔡女則聲稱投資損手，輸了700萬元，要賠償公司600萬元，所以無法歸還11萬元給她。最後，李發現對方封鎖了自己的微信帳號，對方手機也無人接聽。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210405/A62H6KVRCVHVFFZ7PT4RCIK44I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210405%2FA62H6KVRCVHVFFZ7PT4RCIK44I%2F&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLX88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=5a266190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210405%2FA62H6KVRCVHVFFZ7PT4RCIK44I%2F&h=ab2cae00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210405/A62H6KVRCVHVFFZ7PT4RCIK44I/</a>"},{"pid":"dd09c842399451fcea0e61c3d291a15966c5cc40","tid":2476887,"uid":198181,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T00:08:30.000Z","msg":"用微信都係支那人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868f4b1235e447d29192d3615106569f573445cc","tid":2476887,"uid":3270,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTim